  "texts": [
    "1 using strings generated by an LLM and S col.1 using actual spoken utterances from participants through an interactive needs extraction system.",
    "This comparison evaluates the impact of r 1 and provides insights for improving search accuracy in S col. 1.",
    "In S ide.1, 100 user utterances for Experiment 1 and 100 6W1H needs for Experiment 2 were generated by gpt-4o-2024-05-13 [26].",
    "For Experiment 3, 100 keywords from Experiment 2's output were used.",
    "In S col., students and faculty members from the Nakamura Laboratory at Kobe University provided spoken input through an interactive needs extraction system over a one-month period, using the built-in microphone of a Surface Book laptop (Windows 11, 8GB RAM) with speech recognition via the Google Chrome browser's Web Speech API."
